volunteer_experiences.description:
As a mentor, I help students prepare for the labor market: I share my own experiences as a Tilburg University student as well as my professional experience, contributing to students' success in both the educational and professional fields.

For the students, I am a:
- Motivator: I encourage him/her to try new things and take on new challenges;
- Resource: I teach the student how he/she can build a network of professional contacts and also how to maintain these contacts;
- Supporter: I encourage an open and honest dialogue listening and reacting to the needs of the student;
- Coach: I contribute to the student's personal and professional developments making sure he/she commits his-/herself to realistic and feasible goals.
